results.name: a(n) = A253563(A003714(n)).
comment: After the initial terms 1, 2 and 4, all other terms can be inductively generated by applying any finite composition-combination of A253560 and A253550 to 4, but with such a restriction that A253550 may not be applied twice in succession.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10946
xref: Cf. A003714, A055932 (same sequence sorted into ascending order), A253550, A253560, A253563, A122111.
